# 熵防护规则: 强制测试覆盖
# 确保关键代码变更包含对应测试

name: require-test-coverage
severity: warning
description: 修改关键模块时必须包含对应测试更新

triggers:
  files:
    - 'src/session-registry.ts'
    - 'src/im-worker-manager.ts'
    - 'src/approval-manager.ts'
    - 'src/daemon.ts'
    - 'src/plugins/**/*.ts'

conditions:
  - type: file_changed
    pattern: 'src/(.*)\.ts'
    require:
      - 'tests/unit/${1}.test.ts'
      - 'tests/integration/${1}.test.ts'
    skip_if: 'tests/.*\.test\.ts'

message: |
  ⚠️ 检测到关键模块变更，但未检测到对应测试更新

  请确认：
  - [ ] 新增功能有对应单元测试（tests/unit/）
  - [ ] 状态迁移场景有对应测试
  - [ ] 错误场景有对应测试

  运行测试确认：
  npm run test:unit

severity_rules:
  - if: 'commit_count < 3'
    severity: warning
  - if: 'commit_count >= 3'
    severity: error
